{"tid":651590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平文化程度如何？ 毛澤東前秘書李銳：他小學程度","createTime":"2018-05-03T08:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T09:45:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdd5a0242044566f16c89ba39850c200a10e9cc","tid":651590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"剛度過101歲生日的李銳在病床上接受美國之音專訪時，表示與習仲勛交好，並指其子習近平文化程度低，「他小學程度」。<br />\n<br />\n李銳曾任毛澤東秘書、中組部常務副部長，他在美國之音訪問視頻中，提到最後一次跟習近平接觸是在其浙江省委書記任內，當時習宴請李夫妻及女兒，一桌就四人，一桌好飯，好得很。「因為他是習仲勛的兒子嘛，我就講話隨便一點」。在席上，李銳告訴習近平，現在地位不同了，可以講一點有意義的話，應該（向上）講點意見啦。「我那個時候不曉得他文化程度那麼低，你們知道吧？他小學程度。」<br />\n<br />\n散席時，習近平又講，「你可以打擦邊球啊，我哪裡敢？」<br />\n<br />\n李銳表示，當然那個時候也沒有什麼看不起他，因為他是（習）仲勛的兒子。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音詢問李銳對習近平有什麼忠告？李銳沉默一會兒說：「做不到，這個人他現在能接受？（搖頭）不可能，不可能。」<br />\n<br />\n李銳在《李銳口述往事》一書中提及會見習近平寫道：「人有了權以後是會變化的。這樣的人我接觸多了。」<br />\n<br />\n李銳還透露，美國之音曾播過他一些隨便講話的厲害文字。有一次是習上台不久，李銳與一位老友的女兒閒聊，她講了一句：「現在網上就有這樣的話&mdash;&mdash;毛病不改，積惡成習。」李銳說，這段話傳到美國去，美國把它公開，搞得他很麻煩，知道嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3089310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7331%2F3089310&d=gNZmezJ%2F5DQ2Js5h%2BSfEvi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e33aabea\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7331/3089310</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49941c86d894897b04e9a366bfe1b92c2c98f4d","tid":651590,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:38:38.000Z","msg":"獨立思考能力備受考驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b75b201608e90155ac1906e40af44196150a4b","tid":651590,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"天才小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fccf0c5c0f139d3827a7fcd2e8cab25f32ba7fb","tid":651590,"uid":54337,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:01:56.000Z","msg":"小學生可以治國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5527138c3dcb527f19aa5a47e0a7ab142a21eca2","tid":651590,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:05:05.000Z","msg":"知識越多越反動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b22c8e20ab381f89c15dcd66ca8db85bd2830963","tid":651590,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"知識分子其實是最沒有知識的,現在他們認輸了。教授不如學生, 學生不如農民"},{"pid":"dcfc5254a6a9a97d3be144080c22e949266deb3b","tid":651590,"uid":59929,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"小學生贏大學生 <br />\n發展中國家贏超級大國<br />\n這就是我的国"},{"pid":"a82a5692daabca57ba0929f4c08402019968a6b8","tid":651590,"uid":137999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"小學雞"},{"pid":"a3f982535799ad1f29ae0482bacae9d56102c6f8","tid":651590,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"全中國最大黑社會"},{"pid":"9c32ca3e35fcbb2b1174cf2cccfe63d1fed15482","tid":651590,"uid":182314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"越醒越難控制"},{"pid":"bcca7fde7b5e3ca0c32772b8202db9fce38ce418","tid":651590,"uid":62494,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"毛病不改,積惡成習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cec3eee5a751249dec615f365c794282930d1e1","tid":651590,"uid":21896,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bcca7fde7b5e3ca0c32772b8202db9fce38ce418","tid":651590,"uid":62494,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"毛病不改,積惡成習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"r